platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its console-quality looks and streamlined controls, NaturalMotions gorgeous drag racer delivers a deep automotive experience. It starts with more than 85 world-famous cars, each ready to customize to perfection in your quest to rule the streets. From multiplayer matches to smoking rival racing gangs, new challenges wait around every corner. Best of all, CSR Racing's quick, intense contests fit into any gamers schedule.
